[cymru_indicator://<name>]
global_account = Select the Cymru account for which you want to collect data.
interval = Time interval of input in seconds.
index = Select the index in which data should be collected. Only required if \"Collection Type\" is set to \"Index\".
api_type = Select the type of API to collect.
indicator_type = Select the type of indicators to collect.
indicators = Enter the comma seperated indicators.